name: thin felt ring 14k
description:
very nice thin felt ring in 14k solid gold.  the ring is a thinner version of the felt ring and looks beautiful on a summer browned hand.  you could wear it as a single ring or stack multiple of them, in different color metals.  also makes a very good choice for a wedding ring.

each ring is carefully handmade to order, and a unique piece of jewelry since no mold is used.

name: wish tag
description: this super tiny wish tag in solid silver comes on a thin black silk string.  it is an old chinese saying that the person who recieves this tag may do a wish while a loved person hangs the tag around him-her.  by wearing it day and night the tag will fall of naturally and the wish may come true.

name: pear ring 14k
description:
this pear ring is made of 14k solid gold.  you can wear it as a single ring but also looks really beautiful when you stack more of them as the 'points' all fall in there own direction.

each ring is carefully handmade to order, and a unique piece of jewelry since no mold is used.

name: paper ring horizontal
description:
this ring was originally made of paper.  the paper ring comes in two different ways.  as paper is a very natural material the ring has a nice organic look to it.  you can actually see the lines of the cracks in the paper which are transported into the silver.

each ring is carefully handmade to order, and a unique piece of jewelry since no mold is used.

name: felt ring
description:
this ring has the soft looks of felt fabric although it is made of solid sterling silver.  it is very comfortable to wear and makes a perfect wedding ring together with the thin felt ring.

each ring is carefully handmade to order, and a unique piece of jewelry since no mold is used.
